snippet.textDisplay: 💔💔I’m currently in a relationship with someone who I thought was my soulmate and my best friend We wanted a baby so bad and 6 months after trying I ended up pregnant and that’s when everything really went down dude didn’t give two fucks about me or the fact we were having a baby I was so depressed and anxious to later find out I had a miscarriage he was there for me all those times I had to go to the hospital for that miscarriage after we both wanted the baby so badly and he wasn’t there for me I really think it’s his fault for so many reasons idk if I’m wrong for it but he really made me go through so much while I was pregnant it’s hard not to think about it even tho I’m still with him there’s not a day that goes by that I wish I can find my true self again and not have to go through this nd just leave it hurts being in a relationship that’s one sided and being manipulated into thinking your the crazy one nd that they really love you but you know they wouldn’t do the things they do you if they really did .but it hurts more when you stay and you get hurt over nd over because you just can’t leave. I pray on day I can say enough is enough and leave his ass. I mean I’m barley turning 18 to be letting myself go through this I didn’t even consider myself that type of person to let someone do all this to me but one never listens to there own advice the heart says it’s over when it wants too and u can’t control that even if you try breaking up with them every three weeks🤦🏻‍♀️ and  sadly that happens to a lots more people. But I really like that he can share his experience having to be in a toxic relationship. really gives hope I can move on from this one day and I’m not the only one❤️❤️❤️❤️
